\c 10
\s Akaipa anozvikudza pamberi paMwari, asi Jehovha ndiye murwiri
\p
\v 1 Munomirireiko kure, Jehovha? Munozvivanzireiko panguva dzokutambudzika?
\v 2 Pakuzvikudza kwake akaipa anotambudza murombo zvikuru; Ngavabatwe namano avakafunga.
\v 3 Nokuti wakaipa anozvirumbidza pamusoro pezvinoda mwoyo wake, Anoruchiva anoramba Jehovha nokumuzvidza.
\v 4 Nokuzvikudza kwechiso chake, wakaipa anoti, "Haangabvunzi." Ndangariro dzake dzose dzinoti, "Hakuna Mwari."
\v 5 Nzira dzake dzakasimba nguva dzose; Zvamunotonga imi zviri kure kumusoro, haazvioni; Kana vari vadzivisi vake vose, anovashora.
\v 6 Anoti mumwoyo make, "Handingazununguswi; Handingavi panhamo kusvikira kumarudzi angu ose."
\v 7 Muromo wake uzere nokutuka nokunyengera nokumanikidza; Zvakashata nezvakaipa zviri pasi porurimi rwake.
\v 8 Anogara panzvimbo dzokuvanda dzemisha; Pakavanda ndipo paanouraya asina mhosva; Meso ake anovandira asina wokumubatsira.
\v 9 Anovandira pakavanda seshumba panzvimbo yayo; Anovanda kuti abate murombo; Anobata murombo, kana achimukakatira mumumbure wake.
\v 10 Anonyangira, anokotama pasi, Vasina mubatsiri vanowiswa nesimba rake.
\v 11 Anoti mumwoyo make, "Mwari akanganwa; Anovanza chiso chake, haangatongozvioni."
\v 12 Simukai Jehovha; Mwari simudzai ruoko rwenyu; Regai kukanganwa varombo.
\v 13 Akaipa anozvidzireiko Mwari, Achiti mumwoyo wake, "Hangabvunzi?"
\v 14 Mazviona henyu; nokuti munoona kutambudzika nokuchema, kuti muzvibate muruoko rwenyu; asinamubatsiri anozviisa kwamuri; Makava mubatsiri wenherera.
\v 15 Vhunai ruoko rwowakaipa.
\s Kana ari munhu akashata, nzverai zvakaipa zvake, kusvikira musingazozviwani.
\p
\v 16 Jehovha ndiye Mambo	.
\v 1 !
\s nokusingaperi-peri;
\s Vahedheni vakaparadzwa munyika yake.
\p
\v 17 Jehovha, makanzwa zvinodikanwa navanyoro;
\s Muchasimbisa mwoyo yavo, mucharerekera nzeve yenyu;
\p
\v 18 Kuti mutongere nherera
\s neanotambudzwa,
\s Kuti munhu wapanyika arege
\s kuramba achivhundusa.
